cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

This paper deals with analyzing and describing visual textures of fine-grained categories, which is a problem in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also uses deep learning models for texture captioning, which falls under natural language processing (cs.CL). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of orderless pooling and bilinear CNNs, which are techniques commonly used in machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Finally, the paper deals with visualizations and descriptions of images, which is a topic in multimedia (cs.MM).
